snippet.title: Bread & Fred – Launch Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Bread and Fred waddle onto Nintendo Switch today: https://ninten.do/6056YZqgK

Join the adorable duo as they embark on a charming yet challenging co-op journey up the snowy slopes. Prefer solo? Jeff, your pet rock, is ready to roll! 
 
#BreadandFred #NintendoSwitch
